019package com.plotsquared.core.player;
020
021import com.plotsquared.core.permissions.PermissionHolder;
022
023import java.util.UUID;
024
025public interface OfflinePlotPlayer extends PermissionHolder {
026
027    /**
028     * Returns the UUID of the player.
029     *
030     * @return the UUID of the player
031     */
032    UUID getUUID();
033
034    /**
035     * Gets the time in milliseconds when the player was last seen online.
036     *
037     * @return the time in milliseconds when last online
038     */
039    long getLastPlayed();
040
041    /**
042     * Returns the name of the player.
043     *
044     * @return the name of the player
045     */
046    String getName();
047
048}
